<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='226715' id='t-226715'>is being a great dad.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='228892' id='t-228892'>Above all, above all,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='231623' id='t-231623'>the only goal I have in life
is to be a good dad.</span>
</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
 4:06
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='235320' id='t-235320'>I was given the gift of a miracle,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='237869' id='t-237869'>of not dying that day.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='239397' id='t-239397'>I was given another gift,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='241234' id='t-241234'>which was to be able
to see into the future</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='243785' id='t-243785'>and come back</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='245086' id='t-245086'>and live differently.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='247898' id='t-247898'>I challenge you guys
