<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='253589' id='t-253589'>and please don't --</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='255000' id='t-255000'>but imagine, and how would you change?</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='257617' id='t-257617'>What would you get done</span>
