<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='262621' id='t-262621'>How would you change your relationships</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='264592' id='t-264592'>and the negative energy in them?</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='266300' id='t-266300'>And more than anything,
